####Find Cmdlets
#1. update help system
Update-Help -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue
#2. commands that view/manipulate processes
Get-Command "*Process*"
Cmdlet          ConvertTo-ProcessMitigationPolicy                  1.0.12     ProcessMitigations                                                                  
